-No?

1168
00:43:27,071 --> 00:43:28,072
I knew it.

1169
00:43:28,138 --> 00:43:30,507
-Sung-ju has lost his sense of taste.
-He's done.

1170
00:43:30,574 --> 00:43:31,775
No, wait.

1171
00:43:31,842 --> 00:43:34,011
