1178
00:43:47,691 --> 00:43:49,193
I AM THE BEST SERVER

1179
00:43:49,693 --> 00:43:50,861
EXCELLENT JOB

1180
00:43:50,928 --> 00:43:52,730
It's the main dish.

1181
00:43:52,796 --> 00:43:54,098
The main dish.

1182
00:43:54,164 --> 00:43:55,833
This looks so good too.

1183
00:43:55,899 --> 00:43:56,967
Try it with the mushroom?

1184
00:43:57,034 --> 00:43:59,637
-Yes, top it with the mushroom.
