-It looks good.

1192
00:44:15,352 --> 00:44:17,154
-This can't be bad.
-It can't be?

1193
00:44:17,221 --> 00:44:18,956
It just can't be bad.

1194
00:44:20,190 --> 00:44:21,191
It's so good.

1195
00:44:21,258 --> 00:44:22,192
